        <label><h3>PHOENIX CONTACT: Security Advisory for FL COMSERVER UNI</h3></label><br>
        <span class="pull-right">Share: 
            <a href="mailto:?subject=CERT@VDE has released a new advisory&body=VDE-2021-022: PHOENIX%20CONTACT%3A%20Security%20Advisory%20for%20FL%20COMSERVER%20UNI (URL: http://localhost/en/advisories/VDE-2021-022//en/advisories/VDE-2021-022/)" target="_self">
                Email |
            </a>
            <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http://localhost/en/advisories/VDE-2021-022//en/advisories/VDE-2021-022/&amp;text=CERT@VDE has released a new advisory: VDE-2021-022: PHOENIX%20CONTACT%3A%20Security%20Advisory%20for%20FL%20COMSERVER%20UNI">
